  <brief_title>Hartmann vs R/A in Peritonitis by Perforated Diverticulitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Hartmann vs Resection With Anastomosis and Diverting Stoma for Peritonitis Caused by Perforated Left-sided Colon Diverticulitis: a Multicenter Prospective Randomized Study.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
